## 8. Appendix

### Glossary

|  |  |
| --- | --- |
| Term | Definition |
| Due Reviews | KB entries that haven’t been reviewed within their configured review interval (default 90 days) |
| Staleness Score | A 0-1 score indicating how stale an entry is (0 = freshly reviewed, 1 = very stale) |
| Mark Reviewed | Action that resets an entry’s staleness score to 0 and updates last\_reviewed\_at timestamp |
| MCP Tool | Model Context Protocol tool — programmatic interface for AI agents to interact with the KB |

