### Existing API Reference

**Endpoint:** POST /api/kb/entries/{id}/review

**Behavior:** - Sets last\_reviewed\_at to current timestamp - Resets staleness\_score to 0.0 - Returns 200 OK on success

**Already implemented in:** - Kotlin: UxRoutes.kt → handleMarkReviewed() - Node.js: ux-routes.ts → handleMarkReviewed() - Python: ux\_routes.py → \_handle\_mark\_reviewed()

